title: Starbien
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, Beer/Wine, Caribbean, Spanish, Cuban, Latin , Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Fancy paladar open until late at night. Reservations generally required, but you can inquire about seating upstairs near the bar if you don't have a reservation. Very accommodating to vegans offering black beans, rice, fried malanga, plantains, salads and more.
streetAddress: Avenida 29 No 205/ entre B y C, Vedado
